an idl file with this content...

interface Foo {};
interface Bar : foo {}; /* note: 'foo' instead of 'Foo' */

...will produce a headerfile with this content:

// some stuff removed...
/* starting interface:    Foo */
class Foo {
 public:
};

/* starting interface:    Bar */
class Bar : public Foo {
 public:
};

Note that "Bar : foo" became "Bar : public Foo".

